{"word":"G645 - ἀποσπάω - apospáō - ap-os-pah'-o - Draw","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποσπάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apospáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-os-pah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Draw</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உருவு, விட்டுப்போ, இழு, பிரி"},{"paragraph":"to draw off, tear away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G4685 - σπάω - spáō - spah'-o/4685\">G4685</a>; to <i>drag forth</i>, that is, (literally) <i>unsheathe</i> (a sword), or relatively (with a degree of force implied) <i>retire</i> (personally or factiously): - (with-) draw (away), after we were gotten from.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}